00:33:39.496 --> 00:33:40.796 A:middle
with an eye to accessibility,

00:33:40.796 --> 00:33:41.886 A:middle
keep in mind what
you've learned here.

00:33:43.216 --> 00:33:45.136 A:middle
First, accessibility
is about everyone.

00:33:45.736 --> 00:33:48.466 A:middle
It's about making the great
experiences your app provides

00:33:48.466 --> 00:33:50.456 A:middle
